      "author": "GsLogiMaker",
      "description": "## What's Changed\r\n\r\n### New Features\r\n* Add css styles for improved h6 verse display by @GsLogiMaker in https://github.com/GsLogiMaker/my-bible-obsidian-plugin/pull/34\r\n* Add book order setting by @GsLogiMaker in https://github.com/GsLogiMaker/my-bible-obsidian-plugin/pull/35\r\n* Overhaul descriptions of build settings by @GsLogiMaker in https://github.com/GsLogiMaker/my-bible-obsidian-plugin/pull/36\r\n* Add `mybible` codeblock processor by @GsLogiMaker in https://github.com/GsLogiMaker/my-bible-obsidian-plugin/pull/41\r\n* Add documentation for MyBible by @GsLogiMaker in https://github.com/GsLogiMaker/my-bible-obsidian-plugin/pull/45\r\n\r\n### Fixes\r\n* Fix verse range codeblock off by one by @GsLogiMaker in https://github.com/GsLogiMaker/my-bible-obsidian-plugin/pull/30\r\n* Fix chapters not padding in description examples by @GsLogiMaker in https://github.com/GsLogiMaker/my-bible-obsidian-plugin/pull/37\r\n* Fix spaces being trimmed away by conversion from html tags to markdown by @GsLogiMaker in https://github.com/GsLogiMaker/my-bible-obsidian-plugin/pull/26\r\n* Fix bad links between books with padded chapter numbers by @GsLogiMaker in https://github.com/GsLogiMaker/my-bible-obsidian-plugin/pull/44\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/GsLogiMaker/my-bible-obsidian-plugin/compare/1.2.1...1.3.0",
